                    <tr>
                      <td valign="top"><p><font size="2" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><strong>October 21 -24, 2003 OSGi Alliance World Congress </strong></font></p>
                          <p><font size="2" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">The World Congress of the OSGi Alliance will be held this year in Dusseldorf, Germany. A one-day workshop will preceded the three day World Congress.</font></p>
                          <p><font size="2" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><strong><em>For the full program, see:</em></strong> <a href="http://www.osgiworldcongress.com/agenda_main.asp" target="_off">http://www.osgiworldcongress.com/agenda_main.asp</a> </font></p>
                          <p><font size="2" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><strong><em>To register, see:</em></strong> <a href="http://inventures.com/authorize/events/registration/start.asp?id=56" target="_off">http://inventures.com/authorize/events/registration/start.asp?id=56</a></font></p>
                          <p><font size="2" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><strong><em>About OSGi Alliance:</em></strong> <a href="http://www.osgi.org/about/%20" target="_off">http://www.osgi.org/about/ </a> </font></p></td>
